## 3. Structural Decisions
Major restructure needed - replace TODO List MVP with MenuMaster MVP structure covering core restaurant functionality.

## 4. Acceptance Decisions
Accept Database Schema - it meets DoD and has no blockers.

## 5. Assignments
Alex needs to address the security vulnerabilities immediately. Jordan's request for POS Integration Priority decision is valid and needed.

## 6. Questions for User
None - the mission and objectives are clear.

